===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

#(''physiology'') [[Fluid]] that exits the [[body]] through [[pore]]s in the [[skin]] usually due to [[physical]] [[stress]] and/or [[high]] [[temperature]] for the purpose of regulating body temperature and removing certain compounds from the [[circulation]].

====Synonyms====
*(''fluid that exits the body through pores''): [[perspiration]]

